sigma_analysis_results.rule_description: Detects programs that connect to uncommon destination ports
Detects uncommon outbound network activity via Kerberos default port indicating possible lateral movement or first stage PrivEsc via delegation.

attributes.magic: ELF 32-bit LSB executable, ARM, version 1 (ARM), statically linked, stripped
